  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "SDガンダム外伝 ナイトガンダム物語は、SDガンダム外伝 シークザイオン編プロジェクトを基にしたロールプレイングゲームで、SDガンダム外伝 奇跡の伝説の結末から10年後が舞台です。ゼロガンダムは父の死を受けて、サンダークランの聖なる技を取り戻し、父の敵であるバイスガンダムを倒すための旅に出ます。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "SD Gundam Gaiden: Knight Gundam Monogatari is a Role-Playing game, developed by TOSE and published by Angel (Bandai), which was released in Japan in 1991.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "Suda-Doaka World\" is said to be in a different time and place from the present.\nIt was a mysterious world where humans and MS, as well as fairies and monsters, lived in harmony.\n\nOne day, however, the world was transformed into a dark place by the appearance of the Demon King Satan Gundam, who descended with a thunderbolt.\nFinally, the evil's hand extended to a remote kingdom, and the king's beloved daughter, a princess, was kidnapped by Satan Gundam's minions. The king, in his distress, summoned the legendary knight Gundam to his castle and ordered him to defeat the Demon King.\n\n\"I will surely rescue the princess and restore peace.\"\n\nKnight Gundam swore to the king and left the castle with a priest and a warrior.\nWhat stories will the heroes tell at the end of their great adventure?",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb_storyline"
    },
